text: Preobrazhenka () is a rural locality (a village) in Austrumsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 15 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 56 km from Iglino, 18 km from Austrum. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Preobrazhenka
